<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Founder Special Claimed | Refinery Aesthetics</title>
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300;1,400&family=Jost:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

  <style>
    :root {
      --dark:    #1a1a1a;
      --gold:    #c8a96e;
      --gold-lt: #e2cfa5;
      --white:   #faf8f4;
      --muted:   #7a7168;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    html, body {
      margin: 0 !important;
      padding: 0 !important;
      width: 100% !important;
      max-width: 100% !important;
      overflow-x: hidden !important;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      background: var(--dark);
      color: var(--white);
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* ── BACKGROUND ──────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .bg-layer {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 55% at 50% -5%,  rgba(200,169,110,0.16) 0%, transparent 65%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 45% at 10% 110%, rgba(200,169,110,0.07) 0%, transparent 55%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 40% at 90% 110%, rgba(200,169,110,0.07) 0%, transparent 55%);
    }

    /* ── PAGE ────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .page {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 64px 32px 72px;
      text-align: center;
      width: 100vw !important;
      left: 50% !important;
      margin-left: -50vw !important;
    }

    /* ── LOGO ────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .logo {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .logo-word {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(26px, 4vw, 38px);
      font-weight: 300;
      letter-spacing: 0.28em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--white);
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .logo-rule {
      width: 36px;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--gold);
      opacity: 0.65;
      margin: 6px 0;
    }
    .logo-sub {
      font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.45em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    /* ── CHECK MARK ──────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .check {
      width: 56px;
      height: 56px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.5);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 36px;
    }
    .check svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; color: var(--gold); }

    /* ── HEADLINE ────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .eyebrow {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.35em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .eyebrow::before, .eyebrow::after {
      content: '';
      display: block;
      width: 28px;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--gold);
      opacity: 0.45;
    }

    .headline {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(44px, 7vw, 72px);
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.05;
      color: var(--white);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }
    .headline em {
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--gold-lt);
    }

    .subhead {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(18px, 3vw, 26px);
      font-weight: 300;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .rule {
      width: 44px;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--gold);
      opacity: 0.45;
      margin: 0 auto 28px;
    }

    .body-copy {
      font-size: clamp(14px, 1.8vw, 15.5px);
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.9;
      color: rgba(250,248,244,0.68);
      max-width: 400px;
      margin: 0 auto 52px;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    /* ── LINKS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
    }

    .btn-outline {
      display: inline-block;
      border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.45);
      color: var(--gold);
      padding: 13px 32px;
      font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
      font-size: 10.5px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: border-color 0.25s, background 0.25s, color 0.25s;
    }
    .btn-outline:hover {
      background: var(--gold);
      border-color: var(--gold);
      color: var(--dark);
    }

    .btn-gold {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--gold);
      color: var(--dark);
      padding: 13px 32px;
      font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
      font-size: 10.5px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: 1px solid var(--gold);
      transition: background 0.25s, color 0.25s;
    }
    .btn-gold:hover {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    /* ── SOCIAL ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .social-label {
      font-size: 9.5px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(250,248,244,0.25);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .social {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }
    .social a {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 34px;
      height: 34px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.22);
      border-radius: 50%;
      color: rgba(250,248,244,0.30);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    }
    .social a:hover {
      border-color: rgba(200,169,110,0.6);
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    /* ── COPYRIGHT ───────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .copyright {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: rgba(250,248,244,0.20);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    /* ── ANIMATIONS ──────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    .logo     { animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.1s  both; }
    .check    { animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease 0.25s both; }
    .eyebrow  { animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease 0.35s both; }
    .headline { animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease 0.42s both; }
    .subhead  { animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.52s both; }
    .rule     { animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.58s both; }
    .body-copy { animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.64s both; }
    .links    { animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease 0.74s both; }
    .social-label { animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.82s both; }
    .social   { animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.86s both; }
    .copyright { animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease 0.92s both; }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .page { padding: 48px 24px 60px; }
      .links { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; max-width: 280px; }
      .btn-outline, .btn-gold { text-align: center; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="bg-layer"></div>

  <div class="page">

    <a href="https://www.refineryaestheticswi.com" class="logo">
      <span class="logo-word">Refinery</span>
      <div class="logo-rule"></div>
      <span class="logo-sub">Aesthetics</span>
    </a>

    <div class="check">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
        <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <p class="eyebrow">Founder Special Claimed</p>

    <h1 class="headline">You're locked<br><em>in.</em></h1>
    <p class="subhead">Your spot is reserved.</p>
    <div class="rule"></div>

    <p class="body-copy">We've tagged you for the Founder Special waitlist. When we open in May 2026, the first 10 people to schedule and complete their appointment lock in the founding rate for a full year. We'll reach out the moment our doors open.</p>

    <!-- Whitelist nudge -->
    <div style="max-width:400px;margin:0 auto 40px;padding:20px 28px;border:1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.2);text-align:center;">
      <p style="font-size:9.5px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.3em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#c8a96e;margin-bottom:12px;">One quick thing</p>
      <p style="font-size:13.5px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.85;color:rgba(250,248,244,0.65);margin:0;">Two things to make sure you don't miss your opening day call. First, save <em style="color:#e2cfa5;">info@refineryaestheticswi.com</em> to your contacts. Second, if our first email lands in promotions, drag it to your primary inbox and select <em style="color:#e2cfa5;">"Do this for all future messages."</em> Takes 30 seconds and keeps you at the front of the line.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="links">
      <a href="https://www.refineryaestheticswi.com" class="btn-gold">Explore Our Site</a>
      <a href="https://www.refineryaestheticswi.com/services" class="btn-outline">Our Services</a>
    </div>

    <p class="social-label">Follow along</p>
    <div class="social">
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/refineryaestheticswi" aria-label="Instagram" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5"/>
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"/>
          <circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="1" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.facebook.com/RefineryAestheticsWI" aria-label="Facebook" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="copyright">© 2026 Refinery Aesthetics &nbsp;·&nbsp; Bancroft, WI</p>

  </div>

  <script>
    function sendHeight() {
      var h = document.documentElement.scrollHeight;
      window.parent.postMessage({ type: 'resize', id: 'refinery-thankyou', height: h }, '*');
    }
    if (window.ResizeObserver) new ResizeObserver(sendHeight).observe(document.body);
    window.addEventListener('load', sendHeight);
    window.addEventListener('resize', sendHeight);
    sendHeight();
  </script>

</body>
</html>
